description:
As a customer
  I want to receive confirmation of my order
  So that I can be assured my purchase was successful and track my delivery

elements.name: View order confirmation after successful purchase

steps.name: I have opened my web browser
my internet connection is active
I open Home Page
I am logged in as a registered user
I have added "Wireless Headphones" to my cart
I have completed the checkout process
I should be redirected to the shipping details page
I enter my shipping details
I click continue to payment
I should be redirected to the payment selection page
I select Cash Payment as payment method
I click continue to confirm payment
I should be redirected to my orders page
I navigate to my most recent order
I click on it
I should be redirected to the order detail page
I click Print Invoice
I should be redirected to the order invoice page
I click "Download Invoice"
I should see the invoice PDF with my Order ID downloaded

elements.name: Complete checkout with card payment through Stripe

steps.name: I have opened my web browser
my internet connection is active
I open Home Page
I am logged in as a registered user
I have added "Wireless Headphones" to my cart
I have completed the checkout process
I should be redirected to the shipping details page
I enter my shipping details
I click continue to payment
I should be redirected to the payment selection page
I select Card Payment as payment method
I click continue to confirm payment
I should be redirected to the Stripe payment page
I should see the Stripe payment form

description:
As a registered user
  I want to manage my profile information and image
  So that I can personalize my account

elements.name: User successfully uploads a valid profile image

steps.name: I have opened my web browser
my internet connection is active
I open Home Page
I am logged in as a registered user
I navigate to my account profile page
I select the Upload Avatar option
I upload a valid image file profile.jpg
I click on the upload button
I should be navigated to Profile Page
my profile picture should be updated with the new image

elements.name: User successfully updates their profile name

steps.name: I have opened my web browser
my internet connection is active
I open Home Page
I am logged in as a registered user
I navigate to my account profile page
I click on the Update Profile button
I enter a new name "John Doe" in the name field
I click on the Update button
I should be navigated to Profile Page
I should see my name updated to "John Doe"

name: User Profile Management
